Comment: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bam!
Comment: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Comment: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:54.75,orig,,0,0,0,,Haru{Hal}, I have a question.
Comment: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:29.30,orig,,0,0,0,,Uh, hello? Why's she calling you "Haru{Hal}"?
Comment: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.60,orig,,0,0,0,,Since when has she called you "Haru{Hal}"?
Comment: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:19.80,orig,,0,0,0,,All clear here, too.
Comment: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.60,orig,,0,0,0,,To the top! Pronto!
Comment: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:43.40,orig,,0,0,0,,Come and get me!
Comment: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.00,orig,,0,0,0,,...but it wasn't.
Comment: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.40,orig,,0,0,0,,Ranta, you idiot!
Comment: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:26.00,orig,,0,0,0,,Why did you start calling me Haru{Hal}?
Comment: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:03.05,orig,,0,0,0,,...and I was thinking...
Comment: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:06.45,orig,,0,0,0,,...magic can't heal painful emotions either.
Comment: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:08.80,orig,,0,0,0,,But... even though it was painful to hear you talk about it... it was okay.
Comment: 0,0:22:09.65,0:22:10.65,orig,,0,0,0,,That part was okay.

Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Like... this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something, Haruhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you guys all sleep okay last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Nice and soundly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When I opened my eyes, it was morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always like that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't sleep that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually thinking about Manato.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.75,fix,,0,0,0,,I have a question... Haru{Hal}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:56.00,Alt,,0,0,0,,"Haru{Hal}"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you calm right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were on my own, and I knew I could avenge Manato...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd probably rush in headlong with just my dagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like me, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not... true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not alone, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are here, and I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's get out of here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:29.30,fix,,0,0,0,,Hey, hello? "Haru{Hal}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta, shush.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, we let Manato die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll ever forget that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all have to get out of here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have everyone here now, and we have Merry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Priest who let my friends die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And we let our Priest die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So we won't let anyone else die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:01:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry, you feel the same way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never let another friend die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:30.40,Alt,,0,0,0,,Go all... out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.60,fix,,0,0,0,,So, what with this "Haru{Hal}" thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She was calling you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:03:00.55,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating a yesterday filled with scrapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:05.35,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We clear the path to a hopeful tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:20.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder what remains
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:23.65,op/ed,,0,0,0,,in both these tiny hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:30.00,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The voice I raised upwards scattered into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:33.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The reality I've gamed is hazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:36.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,and even if I can't see ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:39.70,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I can keep moving forward on this long road
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:43.80,op/ed,,0,0,0,,if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:50.05,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Connecting a bond covered in dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:56.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We join back to back in the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:04:02.85,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating an answer full of mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:10.85,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will reach out my hands to seek the light, again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Got ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.70,fix,,0,0,0,,Here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. To the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.60,fix,,0,0,0,,To the top! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Exhaust!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.45,fix,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't they coming after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're too obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,These guys know how humans fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Om, Rel, Ect, Krom, Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,They understand our magic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard, you won't get away for hurting Yume!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:24.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,It'll be hard on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru{Hal}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru{Hal}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:09:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection. Heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a hand here! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm as tough as can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,He seems like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Om, Rel, Ect, Well, Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection. Heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Om, Rel, Ect, Well, Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I thought I could get him if I got closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show them that what we've\Ndone so far wasn't for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's barely alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kill or be killed, no offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,No, this can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:09.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is just like how Manato... damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down here, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry? Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... tend to the wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... hurts more than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on the rooftop, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:57.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,That dagger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Yume.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:16.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'd been thinking this whole time about\Nwhat to say to him once this day came.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:27.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,It seems like we spent a long time together...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,...but it really wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:34.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,It was actually pretty short.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,Too short.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,So I kind of know, but I kind of don't know what I want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:47.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,He was friendly, easy to talk to, and smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,He could do anything and was reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,I thought he was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:02.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,But maybe I just didn't realize what his faults were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:06.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,He might have been hiding his flaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:11.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,If we had spent more time together,\Nmaybe I would have seen another side of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,I wish I knew him more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:23.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,I wish I knew more about what kind of person he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:25.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,I wanted more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:30.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,If we had more time, we would've\Ngone through more things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:37.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,Maybe we would've gotten annoyed at each other and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:43.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Maybe we would've disliked each other...\Nor liked each other more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We've become real Volunteer Soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, we didn't have the money to buy our badges,\Nand we had to be frugal with what we spent on food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't know if we could afford lodging for the next day,\Nand we didn't even have enough for new underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I went commando, like a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing underwear now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite everything, we've become proper Volunteer Soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we didn't have the money to buy the badges...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we wanted to buy the badges after\Nsettling things and tying up loose ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we all decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah, it didn't matter either way for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys just kept nagging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.40,fix,,0,0,0,,Stupid Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make such maliciousful remarks at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just be hated more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Dark Knight, so I'm supposed to be hated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "malicious" not "maliciousful," by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, maybe we can give it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you, Manato-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We pooled our money with the money you left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry-san pitched in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:49.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,If you can hear us, you might be chuckling and\Nthinking we didn't have to get a badge for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:55.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,You'd think it was a waste of money, and that\Nwe should've used that money for equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:03.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't listen to you though, whatever you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:05.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,We've become a good party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry, how are your wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I healed them with my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to mend my clothes, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There are holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice if you could mend clothes with magic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Haru{Hal}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem that happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you finally got to avenge your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:26.10,fix,,0,0,0,,About this moniker...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No... that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the first time anybody's called me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Clothes you have to mend by hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:03.05,fix,,0,0,0,,...and magic can't heal painful emotions either...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:04.95,fix,,0,0,0,,..that's what...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.55,fix,,0,0,0,,...I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so painful for us just losing Manato...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you lost three of your friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to talk about it, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There are wounds that even magic can't heal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:21:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:07.15,fix,,0,0,0,,But... even though it was painful to hear you talk about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:08.90,fix,,0,0,0,,...it wasn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.65,0:22:10.65,fix,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:34.80,song,,0,0,0,,When I try touching
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:41.10,song,,0,0,0,,the dry air after a rain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:47.55,song,,0,0,0,,like a sprouting flower
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:54.05,song,,0,0,0,,fragments of memories overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:17:06.65,song,,0,0,0,,The warmth you gave this hand
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:15.70,song,,0,0,0,,led me to a future I can treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:18.30,song,,0,0,0,,always.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:25.30,song,,0,0,0,,I chased your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:30.90,song,,0,0,0,,I wonder when you became so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:38.20,song,,0,0,0,,I will probably find what I searched the vast world for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:45.50,song,,0,0,0,,at the end of this journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:03.40,song,,0,0,0,,The gentle moonlight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:09.50,song,,0,0,0,,and hidden stars smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:15.90,song,,0,0,0,,The falling withered leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:22.20,song,,0,0,0,,draw near and wipe away tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:37.95,song,,0,0,0,,You said everything these eyes see will connect to one path
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:44.20,song,,0,0,0,,as long as you reach
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.70,song,,0,0,0,,the miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:53.85,song,,0,0,0,,I embraced your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:59.35,song,,0,0,0,,Take me to the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:06.60,song,,0,0,0,,A prayer reaching to the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:14.25,song,,0,0,0,,The endless night is over now.
